channel.title: Can't Log Onto My Own Server
channel.description:
Normally, I type in my User and pass, then I leave my IP thing blank cause I'm running the server from my computer. So my runserver.bat is up and I try to log in, but when I press 'login' It just freezes saying "connecting to server". Then after 30 seconds, it says "server must be down" I know its not don cause I'm running it. I've been able to use my server for 3 months and now suddenly this morning this happens.
Help? All I need to know is which file is messed up and I can fix it. (My compiler doesn't say anything unusual btw)
Thanks Play For Keeps
